    <item>
      <title>三菱日联金融集团经纪业务面临失去更多债券承销交易的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/mufg-s-brokerage-at-risk-of-losing-more-bond-underwriting-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三菱日联金融集团与摩根士丹利的投资银行业务面临失去更多债券承销交易的风险，因为金融监管机构可能考虑因该部门分享客户公司的非公开信息而对其进行处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/mufg-s-brokerage-at-risk-of-losing-more-bond-underwriting-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 02:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本零售商永旺放弃三菱日联金融集团的债券承销业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/japan-retailer-aeon-drops-mufg-brokerage-from-bond-underwriting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[永旺株式会社 (Aeon Co.) 表示，已取消三菱日联摩根士丹利证券公司 (Mitsubishi UFJ Morgan Stanley Securities Co.) 安排其计划中的债券销售的资格，因为据报道，该承销商可能因泄露客户信息而面临处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/japan-retailer-aeon-drops-mufg-brokerage-from-bond-underwriting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 02:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险情绪升温，油价涨势止步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于金融市场普遍出现避险情绪，且全球供应强劲的迹象增多，油价下跌，缩减了一周的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 23:30:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下跌，日元在日本央行结果公布前下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国和澳大利亚股市拖累，亚洲股市下跌，而因市场等待日本央行为期两天的政策会议结果，日元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
